  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Altezza Hotel and Spa provides comfortable and contemporary accommodation in <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>. This modern hotel sits looking over the Tarentaise Valley and the peaks of the Mont Blanc Massif. With a central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a>, you have access to the wonderful Paradiski slopes and vibrant resort centre. </p>
<h2>Unwind and relax</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the extensive <a data-udi="umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b}" title="Paradiski Ski Area">Paradiski Ski Area</a>, make the most of the wellness area included for hotel guests. Have a dip in the indoor pool, unwind in the sauna or soothe any aches in the outdoor jacuzzi with mountain views.  There is also a lovely outdoor terrace facing the mountains, it is a great spot to soak up some winter sun. If you want to stay active, even off the slopes, there is also a fitness room with a range of equipment. For a little extra treat, pamper yourself with a treatment or massage with the expert masseuses and osteopaths (pay locally) and then take a moment to revitalise in the rest room with a herbal tea.</p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p>Fuel up for a day of adventures at the varied breakfast buffet, often including a range of sweet and savoury options. Each evening you can enjoy a varied buffet dinner with a variety of starters, hot dishes and desserts - there is often show cooking where meats and fish dishes are prepared in front of you on request. There is also the option to sample Savoyard specialities for an additional supplement - choose from raclette, fondue and pierrade (bbq meats). </p>
<p>The hotel has a lovely bar with an outdoor terrace, if you are around during lunch time enjoy a range of light bites including pancakes and sandwiches. Before dinner you can enjoy an aperitif in front of the fire, and before heading to bed, you can enjoy the relaxed atmosphere with a digestif next to the piano.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Altezza Hotel and Spa making us the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here, all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
